title: Zeit Of The Concords 3/29: White House Gap, Hunter Biden, SMishing, Madison Cawthorn, Hilaria Baldwin, Ezra Miller
itunes:title: Zeit Of The Concords 3/29: White House Gap, Hunter Biden, SMishing, Madison Cawthorn, Hilaria Baldwin, Ezra Miller
description:
In this edition of Zeit of the Concords, Miles and super producer Anna Hossnieh discuss the 7-hour gap in White House call logs, Hunter Biden's tax probe, SMishing scams, Madison Cawthorn claiming DC is an orgy-filled, cocaine-fueled 'House of Cards', Hilaria Baldwin having yet another child, and Ezra Miller getting arrested for disorderly conduct at a karaoke bar.
